item.title: Webclient
item.dc:creator: @dun_dun_dun dun dun dun
item.description:
@dun_dun_dun wrote:

Signup with DropBox its a free uploading site, no money or credit card needed.

And for your question, mediafire would not work, it needs a direct link to it.
